lead_paragraph: AS Monaco survived a late wobble to see off Guingamp 3-2 at home and move into provisional second place in Ligue 1 above Olympique Lyonnais, who host Ajaccio later on Saturday.

headline.print_headline: Monaco Heap Pressure on Lyon in Race for Second
headline.main: Monaco Heap Pressure on Lyon in Race for Second
